hcc_text: Westchester Avenue is a pedestrian high crash corridor (top third for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile in the Bronx)
info: At Westchester Avenue at Sheridan Exwy Service Road, Sheridan Exwy Nb Exit and Westchester Avenue Br, there were 11 injuries in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
intersection: Westchester Avenue at Sheridan Exwy Service Road, Sheridan Exwy Nb Exit and Westchester Avenue Br
